{"tid":1486084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應唔應該繼續同佢一齊","createTime":"2019-08-18T18:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T03:59:54.000Z","uid":208247,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80e947ef4fb7bf4340d989fbe873c82ccae9d635","tid":1486084,"uid":208247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:18:04.000Z","msg":"我係一個唔鐘意被束縛既人亦都好鐘意去玩<br />\n佢就好怕我被人溝而唔想我去玩 <br />\n同中同可以但大學就麻麻(我中學係女校)<br />\n拍左拖十個月 <br />\n我地都好愛大家 但係我覺得有啲嘢淨係依靠愛係解決唔到<br />\n其實我地無咩共同興趣 <br />\n價值觀一開始都唔係幾同<br />\n佢好似想我係佢最後一個女朋友<br />\n但係唔見佢會同我傾下未來既計劃<br />\n佢有少少港女格 我遷就得既都會就曬佢怕佢嬲<br />\n啱啱開始一齊既時候因為價值觀嘈過(我被鬧)好多次<br />\n我都明白係我問題我都慢慢改左好多<br />\n而佢事後都會反省自己 唔會一嬲就衝動鬧我<br />\n雖然依家睇落穩定<br />\n但係我一個月都會有兩三次比佢無意既說話傷害到喊(我比較眼淺)<br />\n我個人比較善忘 關於傷心同嬲既嘢耐左就唔記得清楚<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee2357dd6741667418764edbf064106fe5600f3","tid":1486084,"uid":244851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:19:10.000Z","msg":"Sheshe?"},{"pid":"2919055cecfc940087e092039254b98f966d34e9","tid":1486084,"uid":299371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:19:29.000Z","msg":"男嘅幾歳"},{"pid":"f03849d99dac2c3b6d1acdd47db5f88136cdb43f","tid":1486084,"uid":208247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2919055cecfc940087e092039254b98f966d34e9","tid":1486084,"uid":299371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:19:29.000Z","msg":"男嘅幾歳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"今年19同我年"},{"pid":"306ef94109ee7fd2e08cf83804ccc5400c673e66","tid":1486084,"uid":208247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eee2357dd6741667418764edbf064106fe5600f3","tid":1486084,"uid":244851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:19:10.000Z","msg":"Sheshe?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:24:17.000Z","msg":"佢係仔"},{"pid":"9565e4b75393915b944ab9daeff171e792172797","tid":1486084,"uid":299371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f03849d99dac2c3b6d1acdd47db5f88136cdb43f","tid":1486084,"uid":208247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2919055cecfc940087e092039254b98f966d34e9","tid":1486084,"uid":299371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:19:29.000Z","msg":"男嘅幾歳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"今年19同我年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:29:11.000Z","msg":"19歲你想佢講啲咩未來計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢自己有咩目標有咩想做都未知啦<br />\n價值觀唔夾可以選擇包容互相體量 亦都要尊重對方諗淺 性格唔夾可以磨合 都係睇你有幾中意對方啫"},{"pid":"ca75da1d574664036a7e481cefda781ebc718383","tid":1486084,"uid":299371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:30:48.000Z","msg":"如果因為驚你俾人搶走而干涉你嘅社交圈子咁佢都幾有問題 咩都驚唔好拍拖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f68aceb4f46d2ead9436dd86aa5b39563a1dda","tid":1486084,"uid":208247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca75da1d574664036a7e481cefda781ebc718383","tid":1486084,"uid":299371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:30:48.000Z","msg":"如果因為驚你俾人搶走而干涉你嘅社交圈子咁佢都幾有問題 咩都驚唔好拍拖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:36:27.000Z","msg":"我啲frd都有咁同我講過 但係如果我唔理佢照去玩 我又唔想佢唔開心同嬲我"},{"pid":"9358823ac86c5df68637d755c0bea572c2c1bf93","tid":1486084,"uid":299371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12f68aceb4f46d2ead9436dd86aa5b39563a1dda","tid":1486084,"uid":208247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca75da1d574664036a7e481cefda781ebc718383","tid":1486084,"uid":299371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:30:48.000Z","msg":"如果因為驚你俾人搶走而干涉你嘅社交圈子咁佢都幾有問題 咩都驚唔好拍拖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:36:27.000Z","msg":"我啲frd都有咁同我講過 但係如果我唔理佢照去玩 我又唔想佢唔開心同嬲我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:38:46.000Z","msg"